data.description: Absolutely beautiful updated home with 4 bedrooms!! You'll fall in love with this updated house that includes new roof, shutters, refinished front porch, new flooring and new light fixtures on both levels. Gorgeous kitchen features white cabinets, all stainless steel appliances, wall oven & microwave, stovetop gas range & hood, dishwasher and loads of natural light with an abundance of windows! The main level has 3 bedrooms and an updated full bathroom. Finished basement offers rec room, 4th bedroom with new carpet and 2nd updated full bathroom, newer furnace with a walk-out to the large fenced in backyard. This lovely home is a must see!! All items that stay include...all appliances including stainless steel refrigerator and washer/dryer, kitchen island, security cameras, basement shelving, the portable gazebo area with turf and chairs, and the fire pit in the backyard!
